English:
[DAUDA]
They are in trouble. We must ask for the datacubes now!

Italian.Translation:

Sono nei guai. Dobbiamo chiedere i cubi di dati adesso!

German.Translation:
[DAUDA]

Spanish.Translation:
[DAUDA]
Están en apuros. ¡Tenemos que pedirles los cubos de datos ya!

Russian.Translation:
[ДАУДА]

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
[DAUDA]

Polish.Translation:

Są w opałach. Musimy poprosić o kostki danych!
